	<body>
		<h1>Guacamole</h1>
		<img src=>
		<h5>Guacamole in a bowl.</h5>
		<h4>This is an easy-to-make guacamole recipe that is sure to impress your
			family and friends!</h4>
		<h3>Ingrediants</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>3 avocados</li>
			<li>1 lime</li>
			<li>1 teaspoon salt</li>
			<li>2 roma tomatoes</li>
			<li>1/2 cup diced onion</li>
			<li>3 tablespoons chopped fresh cilantro</li>
			<li>1 teaspoon minced garlic</li>
			<li>1 pinch ground cayenne pepper</li>
		</ul>
		<h3>Steps</h3>
		<ol>
			<li>Mash avocados.</li>
			<li>Juice limes and add to mashed avocados.</li>
			<li>Add salt, tomatoes, onion, cilantro, garlic, and cayenne pepper.</li>
			<li>Optionally, cover and refrigerate for 1 hour to improve flavor</li>

		</ol>
	</body>
</html>
